	    <li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-547400">
	        <div id="comment-547400" class="comment nopin">

                        
            		
            <div class="post-meta comment-meta">
            	<strong>Patricia White</strong>            	 &#8212; 
                <time pubdate datetime="2022-01-09T14:40:20-04:00">
                January 9, 2022 @ 2:40 pm                </time>
                
                <a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-547400" data-commentid="547400" data-postid="30427" data-belowelement="comment-547400" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Patricia White" aria-label="Reply to Patricia White">Reply</a>                            </div><!-- .comment-meta -->

	 
	        <div class="comment-content"><p>I personally don’t like cornbread but must say that it is good.  Family love it repeat cooking for dinner. Best recipe ever </p>
</div>

	        </div><!-- #comment-## -->
	 
	    <ul class="children">
	    <li class="comment byuser comment-author-bake1687 bypostauthor even depth-2" id="li-comment-548049">
	        <div id="comment-548049" class="comment nopin">

                        
            		
            <div class="post-meta comment-meta">
            	<strong><a href='https://bakerbettie.com' rel='external nofollow' target='_blank'>Baker Bettie</a></strong>            	 &#8212; 
