                March 11, 2022 @ 1:16 am                </time>
                
                <a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-549993" data-commentid="549993" data-postid="30427" data-belowelement="comment-549993" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Ny" aria-label="Reply to Ny">Reply</a>                            </div><!-- .comment-meta -->

	 
	        <div class="comment-content"><p>This recipe was horrible 2tsp of kosher salt. Cornbread was salty had to throw it out an make a new batch.</p>
</div>

	        </div><!-- #comment-## -->
	 
	    <ul class="children">
	    <li class="comment even depth-2" id="li-comment-551113">
